### 6. Screen Hook Component (`MyOrdersDetails/index.tsx`)

**Pattern:** Hook Component pattern (logic + UI separation)

**Key Behaviors:**

**A. Data Fetching:**
```typescript
useFocusEffect(
  useCallback(() => {
    if (!hasFocused.current) {
      eventScreenViewV3(...)  // Analytics
      hasFocused.current = true;
    }

